  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dad\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0da2\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc3 \u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca 02\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "02 who attacked Rohitha's and Johnston's houses are caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Western Province South Crime Division says that a woman and a man involved in the cases of looting and looting the houses of Parliamentarians Rohitha Abeygunawardena and Johnston Fernando in Rathmalana were arrested today (24th).",
        "The police say that 25 people who allegedly attacked the houses of the two MPs have been arrested so far.",
        "The police have taken into custody the stolen gas cylinders, a bodybuilding machine, as well as some empty bottles of foreign liquor of the Istram type.",
        "According to the police, the suspects were arrested on the basis of CCTV footage and information received from private informants for attacking the houses and looting the property in Ratmalana Sirimal Uyana area during the riots that took place across the island on the last day of May.",
        "A police officer said that during the questioning of the suspect, he kept and drank the bottles of looted foreign liquor along with the other group who came to attack and drank on the nearby railway track.",
        "The arrested suspect is a 26-year-old resident of Ratmalana Angulana and the suspect is a 45-year-old resident of Ratmalana Mallikarama Road.",
        "The suspect and the suspect are to be produced before the Mt. Magistrate's Court."
      ],
